ibles escenarios en M&#x000e9;xico". <span><span class="ref-journal">Gaceta M&#x000e9;dica de M&#x000e9;xico. </span>2008;<span class="ref-vol">4</span>:285\xe2\x80\x93290.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/18942261" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2765941&amp;issue-id=354895&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Gaceta+M&#x000e9;dica+de+M&#x000e9;xico&amp;title=&quot;La+pandemia+de+influenza:+posibles+escenarios+en+M&#x000e9;xico&quot;&amp;author=P+Kuri-Morales&amp;volume=4&amp;publication_year=2008&amp;pages=285-290&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2765941&amp;issue-id=354895&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div></div></div></div><!--post-content--></div>\n            \n            \n        \n            \n        </div>\n        <!-- Book content -->\n    </div>\n    \n    <div id="rightcolumn" class="four_col col last">\n        <!-- Custom content above discovery portlets -->\n        <div class="col6">\n            \n        </div>\n        \n        <div xmlns:np="http://ncbi.gov/portal/XSLT/namespace" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"><div class="format-menu"><h2>Formats:</h2><ul><li class="selected">Article</li> | <li><a href="/pmc/articles/PMC2765941/?report=reader">PubReader</a></li> | <li class="epub-link"><a href="/pmc/articles/PMC2765941/epub/">ePub (beta)</a></li> | <li><a href="/pmc/articles/PMC2765941/pdf/12961_2009_Article_94.pdf">PDF (258K)</a></li> | <li><a href="#" data-citationid="PMC2765941" class="citationexporter ctxp">Citation</a></li></ul></div></div><div xmlns:np="http://ncbi.gov/portal/XSLT/namespace" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" class="share-buttons"><h2>Share</h2><ul><li class="facebook"><a href="https://www.faceboo